---
title: ’Shroom & Gouda Pork Burgers with Potato Wedges & Garlic Aioli
description: Not to get cheesy, but we’re head over heels for these bodacious burgers. Juicy pork patties are topped with an ultra-savory combo of nutty gouda cheese, buttery sautéed mushrooms and onions, and a dollop of garlic aioli, then tucked into toasty buns. On the side, there’s a heap of crispy potato wedges and more garlic aioli for dunking. If you’re into all-things savory, it’s safe to say you’ll be falling hard for this umami-bomb of a dish, too.
